8422,"uid":165515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"我認同<br />\n趙博士都講過，<br />\n我地200萬人係成個中國黎講都仲係少數<br />\n我地不能太依賴美國戰線"},{"pid":"f4d92e4d6d96d799df46d9f0d50c08e79e8f0232","tid":1698422,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"支那人永遠都係下等人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人反抗就快半年<br />\n你地中國共產黨仲要出政策奶我地鞋底<br />\n先唔理對香港人係唔係真係有用,有冇人真係想去大灣區買樓<br />\n但可以同你地中國人講<br />\n香港人真係又高貴過你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隨便一隻警甴OT幾個月都可以炒高晒你地大灣區既樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得支那人諗盡辦法假結婚投資移民人才移民都想做香港人啦<br />\n<br />\n歡迎轉到微博我先唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1239c8695d0cb65ef6487228ff8598b56429d5","tid":1698422,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:23:03.000Z","msg":"樓主有道理<br />\n詳見：<br />\n微博暴動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697717</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d932c5de4ab10555320de0d121f49ca064664940","tid":1698422,"uid":59195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"大灣區...<br />\n真香港人唔會去<br />\n偽香港人唔願返去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係人都知發展大灣區係引鳩香港人去大陸發展經濟。就算班支那嘈生曬但根本對佢地無損失。反而多左人買樓，令大灣區經濟發展更快"},{"pid":"208aae426c71e8bdbd37439712521f589e243848","tid":1698422,"uid":75684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:40:13.000Z","msg":"我見到果個問左我兩句香港依家樓價幾多<br />\n比完呎價佢睇,佢答&quot;大灣區一定要被香港人炒到爆炸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;  <br />\n睇黎真係好大殺傷力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022639718988b651d613f448696337211e3d9397","tid":1698422,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"18b45f7bb68864964d2e8cae2f81535796894c96","tid":1698422,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"係，但唔使太大期望。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf229ba23b788ebc9075dba22992f9699333ed7","tid":1698422,"uid":330457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:48:07.000Z","msg":"向大陸輸出革命唔係唔得 但要等到佢哋經濟大規模不穩先嚟<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">踩多佢一腳</span></span>先有最大嘅效果"},{"pid":"e914de964b822c2f1d36629ee002d7816c74ed88","tid":1698422,"uid":58948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"香港都未搞好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw一步一步嚟唔洗急 樓主加油"},{"pid":"5464ac2c2e69c08977c88bb0e091f44805a32f36","tid":1698422,"uid":310784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"空氣推"},{"pid":"d4420151a415cfdb3d777a72596fd21ff252c6e4","tid":1698422,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:00:28.000Z","msg":"樓主可以去品蔥交流下,嗰度你應該會搵到好多志同道合既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fed1b1d0981ff437911b1a1288c0cfd62561379","tid":1698422,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4420151a415cfdb3d777a72596fd21ff252c6e4","tid":1698422,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:00:28.000Z","msg":"樓主可以去品蔥交流下,嗰度你應該會搵到好多志同道合既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"我都係鍾意連登多d<img sr